{"name": "jsonschema-extractor", "metadata": {"name": "jsonschema-extractor", "version": "2.0.2", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 5 - Production/Stable", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License"], "home_page": "https://github.com/toumorokoshi/jsonschema-extractor", "license": "", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "\"a framework to extract jsonschemas from a variety of models.\"", "upload_time": 1666674663}, "documentation": ["# jsonschema-extractor\n\njsonschema-extractor is a library and extensible framework for\nextracting [json schema](http://json-schema.org/) from various object and\nprimitives.\n\n```{image} https://github.com/toumorokoshi/jsonschema-extractor/actions/workflows/python-package.yaml/badge.svg\n:target: https://github.com/toumorokoshi/jsonschema-extractor/actions/workflows/python-package.yaml\n```\n\nOut of the box support exists for:\n\n- [attrs](https://attrs.readthedocs.io/)\n- [typing](https://docs.python.org/3/library/typing.html)\n\n## Usage\n\n```python\nfrom typing import List\nimport jsonschema_extractor\nassert jsonschema_extractor.extract(List[int]) == {\n    \"type\": \"array\",\n    \"items\": {\"type\": \"integer\"}\n}\n```\n\n## Attrs-example\n\n```python\nimport attr\nfrom attr.validators import instance_of\nimport jsonschema_extractor\n\n@attr.define\nclass Example(object):\n    integer: int = attr.field()\n    foo = attr.field(metadata={\"jsonschema\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"format\": \"uuid\"}})\n    validator_list: List[float] = attr.field()\n    string: str = attr.field(\n        default=\"foo\",\n        metadata={\"description\": \"This is an description.\"}\n    )\n\nassert extractor.extract(Example) == {\n    \"type\": \"object\",\n    \"title\": \"Example\",\n    \"properties\": {\n        \"string\": {\"description\": \"This is an description.\", \"type\": \"string\"},\n        \"integer\": {\"type\": \"integer\"},\n        \"validator_list\": {\"items\": {\"type\": \"number\"}, \"type\": \"array\"},\n        \"foo\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"format\": \"uuid\"},\n    },\n    \"required\": [\"integer\", \"foo\", \"validator_list\"],\n}\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "jsonschema_extractor.attrs_extractor", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "jsonschema_extractor.attrs_extractor._iterate_validator", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "validator", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "jsonschema_extractor.attrs_extractor._enum_to_values", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "enum_type", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Convert an Enum into a list of values"]}], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "jsonschema_extractor.attrs_extractor.AttrsExtractor", "bases": ["object"], "methods": [{"name": "jsonschema_extractor.attrs_extractor.AttrsExtractor.can_handle", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "typ", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "jsonschema_extractor.attrs_extractor.AttrsExtractor.extract", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "cls", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "extractor", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "typ", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["take an attrs based class, and convert it\nto jsonschema."]}, {"name": "jsonschema_extractor.attrs_extractor.AttrsExtractor._extract_attribute", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "cls", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "extractor", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "attribute", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "jsonschema_extractor.attrs_extractor.AttrsExtractor._extract_attribute_schema_by_type", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "cls", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "extractor", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "attribute", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": 